SQL_STMT_U.val:
select sum(ctr) from (
(select count(*) ctr from PRD_VQMS_Header where pass_date=':1' and pass_time>=':2' and pass_type<>'D' AND LINE=':5') union all (select count(*) ctr from PRD_VQMS_Header where pass_date=':3' and pass_time<':4' and pass_type<>'D' AND LINE=':5') )

select sum(ctr) from ( (select count(*) ctr from PRD_VQMS_Header a where a.PASS_DATE=':1' and a.PASS_TIME>=':2' and exists(select MODELCODE from FRAMEWISEDEFECT b where b.eng_frame_type = a.eng_frame_type and b.chassis_number = a.chassis_number) and a.line=':5') union all
(select count(*) ctr from PRD_VQMS_Header a where a.PASS_DATE=':3' and a.PASS_TIME>=':4' and exists(select MODELCODE from FRAMEWISEDEFECT b where b.eng_frame_type = a.eng_frame_type and b.chassis_number = a.chassis_number) and a.line=':5') )

select sum(ctr) from ( (select count(*) ctr from PRD_VQMS_Header where pass_date=':1' and pass_time>=':2' and pass_type='D' and line=':5') union all (select count(*) ctr from PRD_VQMS_Header where pass_date=':3' and pass_time<':4' and pass_type='D' and line=':5') )
